<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='973' id='t-973'>2014 is a very special year for me:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='4107' id='t-4107'>20 years as a consultant,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='6034' id='t-6034'>20 years of marriage,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='7706' id='t-7706'>and I'm turning 50 in one month.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='10887' id='t-10887'>That means I was born in 1964
