</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:27
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='16437' id='t-16437'>It was a gray November day,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='18155' id='t-18155'>and I was overdue.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='20035' id='t-20035'>The hospital's maternity ward
was really stressed out</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='23518' id='t-23518'>because a lot of babies were born
on this gray November day.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='28023' id='t-28023'>As a matter of fact,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='30145' id='t-30145'>1964 was the year with the highest
birth rate ever in Germany:</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='34571' id='t-34571'>more than 1.3 million.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='36591' id='t-36591'>Last year, we just hit over 600,000,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='39725' id='t-39725'>so half of my number.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 0:52
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='41490' id='t-41490'>What you can see here
is the German age pyramid,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='45321' id='t-45321'>and there, the small black point
at the top, that's me.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='48130' id='t-48130'>(Laughter) (Applause)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='54307' id='t-54307'>In red, you can see the potential
working-age population,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='58440' id='t-58440'>so people over 15 and under 65,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='62689' id='t-62689'>and I'm actually only interested
in this red area.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 1:17
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='66404' id='t-66404'>Now, let's do a simple simulation</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='68447' id='t-68447'>of how this age structure will develop
over the next couple of years.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='72975' id='t-72975'>As you can see,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='74414' id='t-74414'>the peak is moving to the right,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='76713' id='t-76713'>and I, with many other baby boomers,
