<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='93291' id='t-93291'>is already set in stone today,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='96589' id='t-96589'>except for much higher migration rates.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='100141' id='t-100141'>And if you compare this red area in 2030
